data.description: Step inside this Grand Cay home and experience a coastal mediterranean pool home near the beach and Saint Augustine Historic District .   Walking distance to a  new grocery store, restaurants and child care center make this location even more desirable.   No-flood zone too!  Nearby schools, Interstate-95, shopping, golf courses and parks are only few minutes away by car.  This house was a model home for Grand Cay community, so it is full of upgrades and many decorative features. Upon entering, you will be immediately wowed by the large living room with 10' ceilings, large windows and beautiful luxury vinyl plank flooring. A set of French doors to the left lead into the office area that could easily be a 4th bedroom. The living room flows into the spacious dining room area. A short wall partition separates the dining room area from the family room. The open kitchen with breakfast nook offers a relaxing view of the pool and mature trees in the backyard preserve. 3 sleeping rooms are separated from the main area by a long hallway. The primary bedroom view is so breathtaking that you must see it yourself in person. The 2 other bedrooms are also very functional and private. The main feature of the house is the private Floridian backyard patio with  postcard perfect pool and firepit. Yard is completely fenced in and backs up to a wooded preserve for privacy. The whole family will enjoy the pool on hot days, or under the screened-in patio providing shade and ample area to BBQ. The Jasmine garden stretches along the fence line and smells wonderful when blooming. Outside pool shower is convenient too!  This is the ideal Florida dream home.
